cancelMarketSale(address,uint256).details: Cancels an NFT listing on the marketplace and returns the listing fee to the seller

params.itemId: the item ID of the NFT on the marketplace
params.nftContract: contract that the NFT was minted on. Only accepts CHES NFT contract addresses

createMarketItem(address,uint256,uint256.details: Function to list a CHES NFT on the marketplace

params.nftContract: contract that the NFT was minted on. Only accepts CHES NFT contract addresses
params.price: the price of the token in Chain Estate tokens
params.tokenId: the token ID of the NFT on the NFT contract

createMarketSale(address,uint256,uint256.details: Creates the sale of a marketplace item. Transfers ownership of the NFT and sends funds to the seller

params.amountIn: the amount of CHES token the user is supplying to purchase the NFT
params.itemId: the item ID of the NFT on the marketplace
params.nftContract: contract that the NFT was minted on. Only accepts CHES NFT contract addresses

getListingPrice().details: Gets the listing price for listing an NFT on the marketplace

owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.

renounceOwnership().details: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions anymore. Can only be called by the current owner.
